{"tid":1556373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身穿美國國旗外套 中國網民狂轟賣國","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T17:06:12.000Z","uid":51546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9210770e3697b78b003d8113a8bfa0a309a0f13b","tid":1556373,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"中國男籃在今天早些時候離開廣州返回北京，在回到北京之後，隊員趙睿的一件衣著卻引起了廣泛的關注。<br />\n<br />\n在離開廣州抵達北京之後，有不少球迷到現場來迎接中國男籃，而當男籃隊員出現在球迷視線中時，趙睿的外套，引起了注意。<br />\n<br />\n只見雙手都提著東西的趙睿，身穿了一件胸口印有美國國旗、左臂印有USA字樣的白色外套，被圖片社拍到了之後，很快在社交網路上流傳開來。<br />\n<br />\n甚至於，趙睿的名字一度登上了微博的熱搜<br />\n而點開這條熱搜，網友們討論的全是這個事件，絕大部分人都覺得，在這個時間段穿這樣的一件衣服，有些不妥。<br />\n<br />\n有網友表示：「趙睿這衣服，咋想的。。。。」"},{"pid":"1f8f66b2fc55a588e9152b8b7813ff5ca90c76f8","tid":1556373,"uid":304936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"哦 ok"},{"pid":"0c9f9a7ff835c32888212d15d3272d6e13733750","tid":1556373,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"聽聞啲大陸閪好鍾意着Champion FILA 啲紅白藍衫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KK5X0j8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKK5X0j8.jpg&h=b81aea73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OakMTE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOakMTE8.jpg&h=a7384058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有李寧牌唔着，算唔算賣國？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuMwkkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuMwkkD.jpg&h=0e9f26e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"065577858658e75816d8fb9fe9bf0d3fda849bf6","tid":1556373,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"乜9都上到熱投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想紅唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6949fb4165b02aa13d1e40173f806b4d792fee3","tid":1556373,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci